{"tid":1232163,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"怎樣跟喜看tvb家人討論事件","createTime":"2019-06-16T14:45:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T17:46:58.000Z","uid":261448,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b1e2fcd4242d1abbfc76df7bb0bd0ab146d29216","tid":1232163,"uid":261448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:45:03.000Z","msg":"建議大家有堅強既信念，請兼看cctvb news （偷偷看不要令無法理性判斷的人看到）<br />\n<br />\n以他人的矛，攻他人之盾。<br />\n<br />\n好好地令佢地一步一腳印地 拆開cctvb 一直以來的心理建設。<br />\n<br />\n一講到其他事情，拉回最基本，講返條條例有咩問題，最少令佢地一齊align 立此法是惡法！ <br />\n並非如中聯辦說我地為反政府而反例。（我地要先理解佢地聽到d咩野，我地幫佢較返正！）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0cyVxVs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0cyVxVs.png&h=df2d8903&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4zUEZAt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4zUEZAt.png&h=56f06bd5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wFLAxVu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwFLAxVu.png&h=9820b50f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TzxLaHa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTzxLaHa.png&h=2f15f0b4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KxuBhnb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKxuBhnb.png&h=30c7308d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"abcc74b79555f9e00b78e1c6aa00da4f1847f6fa","tid":1232163,"uid":102198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:47:39.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦<br />\n呢d濕鳩你點講都唔會有用<br />\n不如有時間做下文宣仲好啦"},{"pid":"b51c349f9c778fe63c93f8f13a078452075553a5","tid":1232163,"uid":261448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abcc74b79555f9e00b78e1c6aa00da4f1847f6fa","tid":1232163,"uid":102198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:47:39.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦<br />\n呢d濕鳩你點講都唔會有用<br />\n不如有時間做下文宣仲好啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:50:21.000Z","msg":"你做既文宣 目標唔係要遊說依d人咩？"},{"pid":"aa64639f81a2b10246757fd687dc0740c81049db","tid":1232163,"uid":107368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:09:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><br />\n<br />\n繼續做野 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>TVB在反送中報導一事，已經嚴重違反電視通用業務守則中有關「第9章準確、持平及公正」，當中要求「持牌人必須盡一切合理努力，確保新聞、時事節目...的真實資料準確無誤」，以及「持牌人必須確保新聞節目...能夠恰當地持平」，「不可使用謬誤資料或歪曲事實。持牌人亦不應錯誤引導觀眾，以致對節目提及的人士或團體不公平」<br />\n<br />\nTVB在反送中的報導完全扭曲事相，報導嚴重偏袒警方和政府，報導失實 ， 偏頗，例如6月12日的「六點半新聞報道」和「晚間新聞」，完全不播放及不提及：<br />\n1. 警方違法向多名記者開槍，棍打記者<br />\n2. 警方違法瞄準市民頭部發射布袋彈和橡膠子彈<br />\n3. 在沒有任何襲擊下，警方違法向婦孺、伯伯開槍<br />\n4. 警方違法向市民投擲鐵枝、磗頭<br />\n5. 隻字不提一些市民向警方掟水樽垃圾等之前，警方在多處在沒有受到任何襲擊，提出任何警告下，違法突然向市民開槍，不斷發射催淚彈，布袋彈和橡膠子彈，導致局勢快速失控<br />\n6.隻字不提有市民於6月15日於太古廣場因展示示威標語墮樓, 送院搶救後不治的事實<br />\n<br />\n投訴表格：<a href=\"https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=xNvf4PJMmDX7L7bksShbPv7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=dba9e55f\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">日期： 2019/6/12 時間1830 新聞報導</span></span></strong></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0be79e92abf349b71db5656460f34fb05c378e2d","tid":1232163,"uid":261448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa64639f81a2b10246757fd687dc0740c81049db","tid":1232163,"uid":107368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:09:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><br />\n<br />\n繼續做野 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: